"use strict";

var React = require("react");
var Panel = require("react-bootstrap/Panel");
var Row = require("react-bootstrap/Row");
var Grid = require("react-bootstrap/Grid");
var Col = require("react-bootstrap/Col");
var Table = require("react-bootstrap/Table");
var _ = require("lodash");

require("./index.less");

var abilityNames = {
  str: "Strength",
  dex: "Dexterity",
  con: "Constitution",
  int: "Intellect",
  wis: "Wisdom",
  cha: "Charisma"
};

var NpcData = React.createClass({
  displayName: "NpcData",

  propTypes: {
    npc: React.PropTypes.shape({
      description: React.PropTypes.shape({
        name: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        age: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        gender: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        race: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        occupation: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      physical: React.PropTypes.shape({
        hair: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        eyes: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        skin: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        height: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        build: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        face: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        special: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      alignment: React.PropTypes.shape({
        good: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        moralneutral: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        evil: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        lawful: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        ethicalneutral: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        chaotic: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      relationship: React.PropTypes.shape({
        orientation: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        status: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      religion: React.PropTypes.shape({
        description: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      ptraits: React.PropTypes.shape({
        traits1: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        traits2: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      pquirks: React.PropTypes.shape({
        description: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      hook: React.PropTypes.shape({
        description: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      abilities: React.PropTypes.shape({
        str: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        dex: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        con: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        int: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        wis: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        cha: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired
      }).isRequired
    })
  },

  render: function render() {
    if (!this.props.npc) {
      return React.createElement(
        "div",
        null,
        "Loading npc..."
      );
    }

    var majP = this.props.npc.description.pronounCapit;
    var minP = this.props.npc.description.pronounMinus;

    return React.createElement(
      "div",
      { fluid: true },
      React.createElement(
        Row,
        null,
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { xs: 12, md: 6 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "first-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Description"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.description.name,
              " is a ",
              this.props.npc.description.age + " ",
              "years old ",
              this.props.npc.description.gender,
              " ",
              this.props.npc.description.race + " ",
              this.props.npc.description.occupation,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              majP,
              " has ",
              this.props.npc.physical.hair,
              " and ",
              this.props.npc.physical.eyes,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              majP,
              " has ",
              this.props.npc.physical.skin,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              majP,
              " stands ",
              this.props.npc.physical.height,
              "cm tall and has ",
              this.props.npc.physical.build,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              majP,
              " has ",
              this.props.npc.physical.face,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.physical.special
            )
          )
        ),
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { xs: 12, md: 6 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "first-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Personality Traits"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.religion.description
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.ptraits.traits1
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.ptraits.traits2
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.pquirks
            )
          )
        )
      ),
      React.createElement(
        Row,
        null,
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { sm: 12, md: 6, lg: 3 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "second-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Ability Scores"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              Row,
              null,
              React.createElement(
                "table",
                { className: "no-border" },
                _.map(this.props.npc.abilities, function (ability, key) {
                  return React.createElement(
                    Col,
                    {
                      key: key,
                      lg: 12,
                      md: 2,
                      xs: 12,
                      className: "no-right-pad no-left-pad ability"
                    },
                    React.createElement(
                      "tr",
                      null,
                      React.createElement(
                        "td",
                        null,
                        React.createElement(
                          "b",
                          null,
                          abilityNames[key]
                        )
                      ),
                      React.createElement(
                        "td",
                        null,
                        ability
                      )
                    )
                  );
                })
              )
            )
          )
        ),
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { sm: 12, md: 6 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "second-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Relationships"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              React.createElement(
                "b",
                null,
                "Sexual Orientation: "
              ),
              this.props.npc.relationship.orientation
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              React.createElement(
                "b",
                null,
                "Relationship Status: "
              ),
              this.props.npc.relationship.status
            )
          )
        ),
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { sm: 12, md: 12, lg: 3 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "second-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Alignment Tendencies"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              "table",
              { className: "no-border" },
              React.createElement(
                "tr",
                null,
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Good"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.good
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Lawful"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.lawful
                )
              ),
              React.createElement(
                "tr",
                null,
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Neutral"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.moralneutral
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Neutral"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.ethicalneutral
                )
              ),
              React.createElement(
                "tr",
                null,
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Evil"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.evil
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Chaotic"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.chaotic
                )
              )
            )
          )
        )
      ),
      React.createElement(
        Row,
        null,
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { xs: 12 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Plot Hook"
              ) },
            this.props.npc.hook
          )
        )
      )
    );
  }
});

module.exports = NpcData;

  CLASSES: {
    'alert': 'alert',
    'button': 'btn',
    'button-group': 'btn-group',
    'button-toolbar': 'btn-toolbar',
    'column': 'col',
    'input-group': 'input-group',

"use strict";

var React = require("react");
var Panel = require("react-bootstrap/Panel");
var Row = require("react-bootstrap/Row");
var Grid = require("react-bootstrap/Grid");
var Col = require("react-bootstrap/Col");
var Table = require("react-bootstrap/Table");
var _ = require("lodash");

require("./index.less");

var abilityNames = {
  str: "Strength",
  dex: "Dexterity",
  con: "Constitution",
  int: "Intellect",
  wis: "Wisdom",
  cha: "Charisma"
};

var NpcData = React.createClass({
  displayName: "NpcData",

  propTypes: {
    npc: React.PropTypes.shape({
      description: React.PropTypes.shape({
        name: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        age: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        gender: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        race: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        occupation: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      physical: React.PropTypes.shape({
        hair: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        eyes: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        skin: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        height: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        build: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        face: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        special: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      alignment: React.PropTypes.shape({
        good: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        moralneutral: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        evil: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        lawful: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        ethicalneutral: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        chaotic: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      relationship: React.PropTypes.shape({
        orientation: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        status: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      religion: React.PropTypes.shape({
        description: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      ptraits: React.PropTypes.shape({
        traits1: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired,
        traits2: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      pquirks: React.PropTypes.shape({
        description: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      hook: React.PropTypes.shape({
        description: React.PropTypes.string.isRequired
      }).isRequired,
      abilities: React.PropTypes.shape({
        str: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        dex: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        con: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        int: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        wis: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired,
        cha: React.PropTypes.number.isRequired
      }).isRequired
    })
  },

  render: function render() {
    if (!this.props.npc) {
      return React.createElement(
        "div",
        null,
        "Loading npc..."
      );
    }

    var majP = this.props.npc.description.pronounCapit;
    var minP = this.props.npc.description.pronounMinus;

    return React.createElement(
      "div",
      { fluid: true },
      React.createElement(
        Row,
        null,
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { xs: 12, md: 6 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "first-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Description"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.description.name,
              " is a ",
              this.props.npc.description.age + " ",
              "years old ",
              this.props.npc.description.gender,
              " ",
              this.props.npc.description.race + " ",
              this.props.npc.description.occupation,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              majP,
              " has ",
              this.props.npc.physical.hair,
              " and ",
              this.props.npc.physical.eyes,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              majP,
              " has ",
              this.props.npc.physical.skin,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              majP,
              " stands ",
              this.props.npc.physical.height,
              "cm tall and has ",
              this.props.npc.physical.build,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              majP,
              " has ",
              this.props.npc.physical.face,
              "."
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.physical.special
            )
          )
        ),
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { xs: 12, md: 6 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "first-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Personality Traits"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.religion.description
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.ptraits.traits1
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.ptraits.traits2
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              this.props.npc.pquirks
            )
          )
        )
      ),
      React.createElement(
        Row,
        null,
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { sm: 12, md: 6, lg: 3 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "second-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Ability Scores"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              Row,
              null,
              React.createElement(
                "table",
                { className: "no-border" },
                _.map(this.props.npc.abilities, function (ability, key) {
                  return React.createElement(
                    Col,
                    {
                      key: key,
                      lg: 12,
                      md: 2,
                      xs: 12,
                      className: "no-right-pad no-left-pad ability"
                    },
                    React.createElement(
                      "tr",
                      null,
                      React.createElement(
                        "td",
                        null,
                        React.createElement(
                          "b",
                          null,
                          abilityNames[key]
                        )
                      ),
                      React.createElement(
                        "td",
                        null,
                        ability
                      )
                    )
                  );
                })
              )
            )
          )
        ),
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { sm: 12, md: 6 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "second-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Relationships"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              React.createElement(
                "b",
                null,
                "Sexual Orientation: "
              ),
              this.props.npc.relationship.orientation
            ),
            React.createElement(
              "p",
              null,
              React.createElement(
                "b",
                null,
                "Relationship Status: "
              ),
              this.props.npc.relationship.status
            )
          )
        ),
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { sm: 12, md: 12, lg: 3 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { className: "second-row-height", header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Alignment Tendencies"
              ) },
            React.createElement(
              "table",
              { className: "no-border" },
              React.createElement(
                "tr",
                null,
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Good"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.good
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Lawful"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.lawful
                )
              ),
              React.createElement(
                "tr",
                null,
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Neutral"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.moralneutral
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Neutral"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.ethicalneutral
                )
              ),
              React.createElement(
                "tr",
                null,
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Evil"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.evil
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  { className: "width-thin" },
                  React.createElement(
                    "b",
                    null,
                    "Chaotic"
                  )
                ),
                React.createElement(
                  "td",
                  null,
                  this.props.npc.alignment.chaotic
                )
              )
            )
          )
        )
      ),
      React.createElement(
        Row,
        null,
        React.createElement(
          Col,
          { xs: 12 },
          React.createElement(
            Panel,
            { header: React.createElement(
                "div",
                null,
                "Plot Hook"
              ) },
            this.props.npc.hook
          )
        )
      )
    );
  }
});

module.exports = NpcData;
